The UNESCO World Heritage Centre is pleased to announce the selected projects of the World Heritage Volunteers (WHV) 2025 Campaign, under the theme of &nbsp;‘World Heritage Volunteers 2026 - Working on the Future'.
86 action camp projects&nbsp;will be implemented from April to December 2026 at&nbsp;81 World Heritage properties and sites on the Tentative Lists, by&nbsp;68 organizations&nbsp;in&nbsp;36 countries&nbsp;around the globe.&nbsp;
